{"tid":232101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係波鞋街允x好似買到流野","createTime":"2017-05-06T13:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T17:35:31.000Z","uid":114102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"121331c288ad096706968808fd8cdb844c7eadd5","tid":232101,"uid":114102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"事源我今年新年前就係波鞋街允x買左對air max，點知著到宜家唔夠兩個月對鞋氣墊後面居然爛，同埋我唔係成日著。其實著左第一個禮拜對鞋污糟左，我用清水抹佢居然甩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時因為有fd係入面做.7折左都500幾，無諗過著兩個月就變到甘😿<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8woEqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8woEqw.jpg&h=6101b720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hX2o2K4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhX2o2K4.jpg&h=b3cb99e6&s={SIZE}\" /> 各位絲巴打求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9020099324e16b1819e7659b2b59658e9f19f699","tid":232101,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"如果係賣假鞋 正仆街"},{"pid":"6b64d6fc55d198618414545a59163fb11c10ed08","tid":232101,"uid":114102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係賣假鞋 正仆街</blockquote><br />\n我自己都唔知啊，但我上次同款唔同色著左兩年都唔會甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33f3b916404b431a2051dbf19f5f6c273a8a711","tid":232101,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:46:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb255c25d590165934c64b261df213a8d42072b7","tid":232101,"uid":30487,"like":0,"disli